about.summary: Tools for performing model selection and model averaging. Automated model selection through subsetting the maximum model, with optional constraints for model inclusion. Model parameter and prediction averaging based on model weights derived from information criteria (AICc and alike) or custom model weighting schemes.

name: r-mumin
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.47.1" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-mumin
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/MuMIn_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/MuMIn/MuMIn_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 1223b5ada6f7d58220ac0267fa3473993190742646cbbb3dfe63895e61621af6

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base >=4.2.0
    - r-matrix
    - r-nlme
  run:
    - r-base >=4.2.0
    - r-matrix
    - r-nlme

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('MuMIn')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('MuMIn')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=MuMIn
  license: GPL-2.0-only
  summary: Tools for performing model selection and model averaging. Automated model selection through subsetting the maximum model, with optional constraints for model inclusion. Model parameter and prediction averaging based on model weights derived from information criteria (AICc and alike) or custom model weighting schemes.
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file: {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - jacodela
